values: soooooooo, lately my life is starting to slow down. on saturday i had a bowling match out in oxford and my team won by 3 points it was so close!! then after that i just stayed around the house and then went with my dad to pick up dinner. right after dinner i was going to get ready for work and my manager called and said that i did not have to come in to work because we were so slow. i was so happy. then on sunday i hung out with jessica for most of the day. she got her car stuck in the ditch so my dad had to pull her out. it was so funny. then i went to the movies around 7 with tiffany, her cuz, my friend and josh. it was so fun. we saw hostel. big mistake. by the end of the movie, all of us girls felt like we were going to throw up. but ya, a lot happened between me and josh at the movies and i am going to talk to him today about what is going on between us. well that is about it for now. i have to go get ready to go to the dentist. peace.

hey guys. i have been sooooo busy with bowling lately, i am going crazy!!! last week i had practice on tuesday, thursday and friday. and then on saturday i went down to westland with the varsity girls for a tournament and today i had my match. i can not take it any more. along with bowling, i have work and all my meetings. this week is going to be hard but i can make it. there is always good along with the bad!! 


FUNNY STORY!!!
yesterday night after i got home from work (9:30) me and my dad went to pick up my sister and her friends from the movies. when we got there we saw to guys sitting in this little car and we thought nothing of it. when we were sitting there waiting for my sister and her friends, they drove by eating pizza looking for someone. just when my sister and her friends got in the car, they drove by again, and i honked the horn and waved. they kept driving for a couple of seconds and then they decided to back up and they rolled their window down and they were trying to talk to us. i told my dad to floor and and we left. i looked behind us and they were following us. my dad started to speed up and so did they. we finally lost them when we turned on to M-59. thank god. i learned my lesson. NEVER HONK THE HORN AT TWO GUYS IN A LITTLE CAR AT THE MOVIES!!!! lol.

well that is it for now. i am going to go study for some finals. peace!!

hope your team wins the football game keith. we missed you at dinner. maybe you can come next time.

hey guys. i just woke up from a long needed nap. i have been so busy lately i just want to scream. between school, work, bowling and my friends, i do not have that much time to myself, but that is ok because i have been having the time of my life with my friends. I LOVE YOU GUYS. YOU ARE THE BEST. this week is going by so fast. last night was a blast. after i got home from bowling practice, i ate dinner and then i went to jessie's house. at 7:00 we drove up to K-Mart and met Keith and he followed us back to jessie's house and we watched wrong turn. that was a good movie. after that i came home and did my homework then i went to bed. tonite i was going to go out to dinner with jessie and keith but i have to sell 50/50 tickets for bowling with aaron and tony. but i can not wait cuz tiffany is coming up to see me. well that is it for now. i have to go start dinner, so i can eat with my family before i leave. peace!!

hope you feel better josh. sorry i could not come over last night. luv ya.

hey guys, what's up????? HAPPY NEW YEAR!!!! i just got home and i am working on my paper for career connections. last night was soooooooo much fun. after work jessie picked me up and we went to chris and larry's house for a small party. it was a blast. montea and her family were there along with her neighbor keith. we got to their house at like 8:30 and we did not leave till a little after one. we played fose ball, air hockey, and ping pong. my parents were at another party but they still called to wish me a happy new year. after we left chris and larry's house, jessie and i went to my house to get some clothes so i could stay the night at her house and then we went to motnea's house to watch a movie with her, her sister keisha and her neighbor keith. it was a blast. we did not get back to jessie's house till 4:30 in the morning. so, that was my new year's eve. hope everyone else had as much fun as i did.

hey guys, sorry i have not written in a long time but i have been very busy and stressed out. the first official day of break, i had to sell 50/50 tickets for bowling and i come home to a street full of cops. i later found out that my neighbor killed himself in the garage. then on christmas i have a great time until i had to go to my grandparents and see my "cousin" jenny who i only see once a year. then i found out that my cousin is getting married this week. i am so excited. i hope they find a judge to marry them though before donaven has to go to iraq. so as oyu can see, i have been really stressed out and busy because the first day back to school i have a 5 page paper due with a visual. but i am exicted because i am going to the movies tonite to see fun with dick and jane. i can not wait. well that is about it. i have to go get ready cuz crystal will be here soon to work on our visual. HAPPY BIRTHDAY JOSH!! 
peace.

hey guys whats up?? today started out bad got really good then got bad again. i dont know whether i should be happy about what happened at lunch or sad about what i just found out?? who knows. lifes a bitch and then you die so i better get used to things. but that is all for now. i have to go get ready for work. peace!

hey guys, whats up?? not to much here. i am at my grandparents house with my cuz. i just got back from the movies. i saw "just friends" with aaron, gusko and my cuz. it was really good i was just bummed because josh did not come, but there is always next time. soooo, early this morning i had to go out to oxford for my bowling match. IT SUCKED SO BAD. the night before they stripped to lanes instead of putting oil down. that made us start our match an hour late. i bowled like SHIT and i was getting really pissed off at one of my teamates because she was trying to coach everyone and was yelling at me over little things. but that is ok because i got both of my points and we won our match 27 to 3. i was sooooooooo happy. well thats it for now. i am going to go call matt. peace out. luv ya guys.

soo, i just got off the phone with julie and she was telling me how i should update my journal so that is what i am duing. i have not been home from work that long, but i am sure glad to be home. i hate my assitant manager and all the burned fingers. lol. i am so excited for this weekend. saturday morning i have a bowlig match up in oxford (hopefully me and my girls actually get some points this time) and then i get to go to the movies with my friends, and then i am going to my grandparents house to stay the night with my cuz. then on sunday i get to go to gregy and cindy's house for a mexican christmas dinner. well that is it for now. i have to go get in the shower and get all the pizza sauce and flour off me. peace out.

Hey guys. Whats up? I am kinda new at this so it is going to take me awhile to get use to this. So, I just got done putting up the christmas tree and talking on the phone to Pedro and Julie. HI JULIE I LOVE YOU. But besides that I had a great thanksgiving. Well thats it for now. Hope everyone had a great thanksgiving.
